Titolo: Case Closed: The Mirapolis Investigation

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Case Closed: The Mirapolis Investigation, known in Japan as Meitantei Conan: Tsuioku no Mirage (名探偵コナン 追憶の幻想（ミラージュ）, Meitantei Konan: Tsuioku no Mirāju, lit. "Detective Conan: Mirage of Remembrance"), is a video game for the Wii. It is based upon the popular anime and manga series Case Closed by Gosho Aoyama. Players use the Wii Remote to find clues and solve the cases.

Genere: Adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
